<HL>
   Bird Plans a Private Offering
</HL>
<DATE>
06/28/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   BIRD
</CO>
<LP>
   WESTWOOD, Mass. -- Bird Corp., a new holding company for
Bird Inc., a building materials distributor, said it plans to
raise capital with a private offering of a 40% interest in
its housing group unit.
   The offering is part of a five-year growth plan for Bird
to fuel the company's core building materials business and
expand into the environmental business.
